sql:
SELECT SUM(reward_amount) AS total_rewards
FROM staking_rewards
WHERE staking_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- A "bounty" refers to the total rewards earned (i.e., total_rewards > 1000); 
- A "top-performing node" refers to a node with a high total reward amount; 
- A "prosperous year" refers to the year 2022.

sql:
SELECT node_id
FROM node_performance
WHERE uptime > 99.0;

SELECT name
FROM nodes
WHERE balance = (SELECT MAX(balance) FROM nodes);

SELECT node_id, SUM(totalDelegated) AS total_delegated_sum
FROM staking
GROUP BY node_id;

external_knowledge:
Navigator of the validator nodes: Refers to a node operator managing a node of type 'validator'; 
Naviagted: Refers to the action of operating or managing something;
Reaped more than 10,000 units of rewards: More than 10,000 units of staking rewards earned;
Harvesters: Refers to those who have earned or gained something (in this case, staking rewards).
